messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图识别准确性",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "reason": "输出 intent=4001、intent_name=“其他意图”，不符合用户营销规划意图预期"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模型的分类逻辑或提示词未能覆盖“NBEV”和“理财师/产品方案优化”等营销规划关键要素，导致将用户请求误判为其他意图，未能输出正确的营销规划意图码。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "execution_trace.intent_recognition.evidence",
          "detail": "actual_stage=non_agent, expected_stage=intent"
        },
        {
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0]",
          "detail": "intent=4001, intent_name=“其他意图”"
        },
        {
          "source": "judge_result.fulfillment_assessment",
          "detail": "意图识别准确性未满足，score=0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "阶段路由正确性",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "reason": "错误意图导致后续阶段路由异常"
        },
        {
          "stage": "path_dispatch",
          "reason": "依据错误意图分发至 non_agent 路径，未进入营销规划处理阶段"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "因意图识别将请求标记为“其他意图”，path_dispatch 无法匹配到营销规划路由规则，整个对话落入 non_agent 阶段，未能实现任何营销规划功能。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "execution_trace.path_dispatch.evidence",
          "detail": "expected_path_types=[], actual_path_types=[]"
        },
        {
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0]",
          "detail": "stage=non_agent"
        },
        {
          "source": "judge_result.fulfillment_assessment",
          "detail": "阶段路由正确性未满足，score=0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "reason": "实际输出为 non_agent，与参考合约要求 expected_stage=intent 不符"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "参考合约要求意图识别后进入 intent 阶段，但意图识别模块输出的阶段为 non_agent，直接违背合约预期。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "reference_contract",
          "detail": "expected_stage=intent, scenario=intent_recognition"
        },
        {
          "source": "planning_output_probe",
          "detail": "expected_stage=intent, actual_stage=null, stage_match=false"
        },
        {
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0]",
          "detail": "stage=non_agent"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "description": "意图识别模型错误输出 intent=4001 和 stage=non_agent，是导致下游失败的最早阶段"
    },
    {
      "stage": "path_dispatch",
      "description": "未能在分发过程中纠正错误阶段，但根因仍在前序意图识别"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段是 intent_recognition。该阶段对包含“NBEV目标缺口”“增加理财师”“优化产品方案”等营销规划关键词的用户请求，错误地分类为意图 4001（其他意图）并设定 stage=non_agent，使得后续 path_dispatch、planning_function 等全部背离预期流程，最终仅输出占位文本“卡片生成完成”，未提供任何业务内容。",
  "evidence": [
    "execution_trace 中 intent_recognition 的实际阶段 (non_agent) 与预期阶段 (intent) 不符",
    "extracted_output 确认最终意图为 4001（其他意图）且阶段为 non_agent",
    "planning_output_probe 显示 stage_match=false，actual_stage 缺失",
    "judge_result 判定意图识别准确性和阶段路由正确性均未满足"
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

